&lt;Siemens AG's> U.S. subsidiary,Siemens Public Switching Systems Inc said two existing plantshave been selected to allow immediate start up of manufacturingon an interim basis of EWSD digital central office switchingsystems in the U.S.    The company said the two facilities, one in Cherry Hill,N.J., the other in Hauppauge, N.Y., will be used while arigorous review process for selecting a facility devoted onlyto EWSD manufacturing continues.    Siemens Public is part of Siemens Communication SystemsInc, also headquartered in Boca Raton. Reuter&#3;